Package: fwa.connect
Title: Simplify Stream Network Analyses
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Chris", "Madsen", email = "chris.madsen@bc.gov.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains a large data file that describes a 2-columned table that identifies streams using the FWA_WATERSHED_CODE field from the BC Data Catalogue's Freshwater Atlas. One column indicates upstream and the other downstream streams.
